snippet.title: JellyCast #01: Cutie Beginnings
snippet.description:
In the first episode of the Alchemic Cutie JellyCast, Sebastien and Thomas talk about who they are, how they met, and how Alchemic Cutie began development. They also talk about getting into game development and share some details on the game.

Website: https://alchemiccutie.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/alchemiccutie
Facebook: https://facebook.com/alchemiccutie
Imgur: https://imgur.com/user/alchemiccutie
